## Development ðŸ‘©â€ðŸ’»ðŸ‘¨â€ðŸ’»

### Requirements

- Python 3.11+
- Poetry

### Setup

Clone the repository and install the dependencies:

```sh
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/asgi-request-duration.git
cd asgi-request-duration
poetry install
```

### Running Tests ðŸ§ª

You can run the tests using `pytest`:

```sh
poetry run pytest
```

